相放生佢<br />\n想搵佢個廣告訂位page出黎先"},{"pid":"fb28891d6e91f8dc06394fd41bfba9b6e0731d6f","tid":629774,"uid":23786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"1823開file一定要做"},{"pid":"75481cd544f557acecf8ff376aa99d26c94412cd","tid":629774,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"喺親戚屋企見過有疑似自由行去佢嗰層住<br />\n用咗上面條link 投訴<br />\n隔幾日就見到有房署嘅人上去㩒門鐘調查"},{"pid":"ea6fdd8c42bff56c471633cddb7453af337d8e49","tid":629774,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:17:54.000Z","msg":"1823 + ombudsman佢個處理程序"},{"pid":"f29f6ff3f9b7c9282e22e49b9c3580b14d55305a","tid":629774,"uid":59289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:33:41.000Z","msg":"係咪觀塘 鯉XX 前排有人拖喼問我路"},{"pid":"73744fcccb29f59b66ebb5b1c6e45ec646d0e620","tid":629774,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"香港的《旅館業條例》，出租出期少於連續28天才要申請旅館牌照，違法罰則為最高罰款20萬港元及監禁兩年，但一般情況下，被控經營無牌旅館"},{"pid":"3059c02f01919dcaa68b1cca6d8a64dc2a2da075","tid":629774,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"管理及經營無牌旅館者被判罰<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n　　​ 一名男子及五名女子因觸犯《旅館業條例》，今日（十一月八日）在九龍城裁判法院被判罰款7,000元至13,000元。<br />\n<br />\n　　案情透露，民政事務總署轄下牌照事務處（牌照處）人員去年十月至今年四月分別巡查位於九龍上海街、通菜街、廣東道、砵蘭街及土瓜灣道六所懷疑無牌旅館時，喬裝客人，並成功以時租或日租形式租住上述處所的房間。根據牌照處的紀錄，上述處所在巡查當日均未獲發牌照，負責管理及經營上述處所的男女因而被控違反《旅館業條例》第5（1）條。<br />\n<br />\n　　民政事務總署發言人強調，經營或管理無牌旅館均屬刑事罪行，一經定罪會留有案底，最高可被處罰款200,000元及監禁兩年。<br />\n<br />\n　　發言人呼籲市民如發現懷疑違規經營的旅館，請即致電牌照處的舉報熱線（電話︰2881 7498）、電郵至hadlaenq@had.gov.hk、於牌照處網頁（<a href=\"http://www.hadla.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hadla.gov.hk&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=47658791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hadla.gov.hk</a>）下載表格，填妥後傳真至2504 5805，或透過「香港持牌旅館」的流動手機應用程式，向牌照處舉報。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n2017年11月8日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間15時40分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府網搵的"},{"pid":"58eede4ae36bee6a88760da5ee902875ac75ef07","tid":629774,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>保安無check咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>公屋洗乜check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一句唔該就開門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>咪on9啦，一個好陌生嘅人佢唔會開門架<br />\n雖然佢地真係廢，但直少未見過嘅人，佢地係唔會開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>咁可能你果邊既保安有心做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我入親朋友果邊既公屋都冇人問過我上邊幾樓留資料</blockquote><br />\n住戶少咪會問。有啲兩座同一個入口，好多人出入，基本上認唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386c2fc7c35e5d61580b75227b132a02c40fe5db","tid":629774,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"直接找民政 會唔會好d<br />\n<br />\n房署 未必會檢控"},{"pid":"6977256705edd38e4eabceef1290824c8d05fb66","tid":629774,"uid":62554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:46:39.000Z","msg":"send email 去1823，一定要跟進，仲會有書面回覆"},{"pid":"17c8bf51a7d3f7fbaba4e832597247e9d1f76bdd","tid":629774,"uid":81756,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba9e214854cbf2011fad888956ad31fe5e3ae6d","tid":629774,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17c8bf51a7d3f7fbaba4e832597247e9d1f76bdd","tid":629774,"uid":81756,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:46:4